	(MethodInvocation target_pointer): new ivar.
	(MethodInvocation sel_pointer): new ivar.
	(VoidFunctionInvocation): New class.
	(ObjectFunctionInvocation): New class.

	* src/objects/Invoking.h: Make -invoke methods return void.

